  <_name>To Do</_name>
  <_summary>Task manager for GNOME</_summary>

  <description>
    <_p>
      GNOME To Do is a task management application designed to integrate with GNOME. It
      is extensible through plugins and supports custom task providers.
    </_p>
  </description>

